-- EYE BRUSHES
((SELECT id FROM brands WHERE slug='sigma-beauty'),14,'E25 Blending Brush','sigma-e25-blending','Tapered blending brush for diffused eye looks.','Sigma E25 is a medium-density tapered blending brush that builds and blends eyeshadow on the lid and crease. The domed tip is perfect for cut crease techniques and seamless blending.',20.00,'SIG-BRU-E25',75,true,false,ARRAY['brush','eye','sigma','blending','crease']),
((SELECT id FROM brands WHERE slug='mac'),14,'217S Blending Brush','mac-217s-blending','The #1 eye blending brush — a cult classic.','The MAC 217S is the most iconic eye blending brush in the world. The tapered, rounded tip blends and diffuses eyeshadow seamlessly through the crease for a perfectly blended, professional finish.',28.00,'MAC-BRU-217S',100,true,true,ARRAY['brush','eye','mac','217','blending','classic']),
((SELECT id FROM brands WHERE slug='morphe'),14,'M330 Firm Blending Fluff Brush','morphe-m330-fluff','Firm fluff brush for precise lid packing and blending.','Morphe M330 is a firm, slightly tapered fluff brush ideal for packing eyeshadow onto the lid and blending through the crease. Dense enough for intense colour payoff, soft enough for seamless blending.',10.00,'MPH-BRU-M330',120,true,false,ARRAY['brush','eye','morphe','fluff','lid']),
((SELECT id FROM brands WHERE slug='real-techniques'),14,'Eye Shade + Blend Set','rt-eye-shade-blend-set','2-piece eye set: shader and blending brush.','Real Techniques Eye Shade + Blend Set includes a flat shader brush for packing colour onto the lid and a soft blending brush for diffusing and blending eyeshadow through the crease.',18.00,'RT-BRU-ESB',90,true,false,ARRAY['brush','eye','real-techniques','set','shader']),
((SELECT id FROM brands WHERE slug='urban-decay'),14,'Good Karma Eyeshadow Brush','ud-good-karma-brush','Cruelty-free all-over lid shader brush.','Urban Decay Good Karma Eyeshadow Brush uses 100% cruelty-free Taklon fibres to pack eyeshadow onto the lid with intense colour payoff. The flat paddle shape covers the entire lid in one sweep.',25.00,'UD-BRU-GKB',60,true,false,ARRAY['brush','eye','urban-decay','shader','cruelty-free']),
((SELECT id FROM brands WHERE slug='charlotte-tilbury'),14,'Eye Blend Brush','ct-eye-blend-brush','Luxury blending brush for seamless eye transitions.','Charlotte Tilbury Eye Blend Brush features ultra-soft natural and synthetic blend fibres on a weighted handle. The tapered dome blends and diffuses eyeshadow seamlessly for professional-finish eye looks.',38.00,'CT-BRU-EBL',45,true,false,ARRAY['brush','eye','charlotte-tilbury','blending','luxury']),
-- LIP BRUSHES
((SELECT id FROM brands WHERE slug='mac'),14,'316 Lip Brush','mac-316-lip-brush','Precision flat tapered brush for lipstick application.','MAC 316 Lip Brush has a flat, tapered ferrule that delivers precise lipstick and lip gloss application. The firm bristles define the cupid''s bow and corners of the mouth with accuracy.',22.00,'MAC-BRU-316',80,true,false,ARRAY['brush','lip','mac','precision']),
((SELECT id FROM brands WHERE slug='sigma-beauty'),14,'L05 Lip Brush','sigma-l05-lip-brush','Tapered lip brush for precise liner and lipstick application.','Sigma L05 Lip Brush features a tapered ferrule that applies lip liner and lipstick with precision. The pointed tip allows for an exact cupid''s bow outline while the body of the brush fills in colour evenly.',16.00,'SIG-BRU-L05',70,true,false,ARRAY['brush','lip','sigma','tapered','precision']),
-- BRUSH SETS
((SELECT id FROM brands WHERE slug='sigma-beauty'),14,'Complete Kit 12 Essential Brushes','sigma-complete-kit-12','12 must-have face and eye brushes in a signature roll.','Sigma Complete Kit contains 12 essential face and eye brushes to create any makeup look. Housed in Sigma''s signature black roll case, the kit includes SigmaTech fibres that are vegan and anti-bacterial.',169.00,'SIG-BRU-CK12',30,true,true,ARRAY['brush-set','sigma','complete','essential','kit']),
((SELECT id FROM brands WHERE slug='real-techniques'),14,'Everyday Essentials Set','rt-everyday-essentials','5-piece everyday brush set for full face application.','Real Techniques Everyday Essentials Set includes 5 essential brushes for a complete face look: foundation, blush, detailer, shader and blending brushes. Ultra-plush synthetic fibres apply makeup flawlessly.',30.00,'RT-BRU-EES',85,true,true,ARRAY['brush-set','real-techniques','everyday','affordable','5-piece']),
((SELECT id FROM brands WHERE slug='morphe'),14,'Jaclyn Hill Vault Artistry Brush Collection','morphe-jaclyn-hill-vault','25-piece professional artistry collection with Jaclyn Hill.','The Morphe x Jaclyn Hill Vault is a 25-piece professional brush collection designed by beauty superstar Jaclyn Hill. From face to eye, every brush delivers professional artistry at an accessible price point.',98.00,'MPH-BRU-JHV',40,true,true,ARRAY['brush-set','morphe','jaclyn-hill','professional','25-piece']),
((SELECT id FROM brands WHERE slug='it-cosmetics'),14,'Heavenly Luxe 8-Piece Brush Set','itc-heavenly-luxe-8pc','8 essential Heavenly Luxe brushes for face and eye.','IT Cosmetics Heavenly Luxe 8-Piece Brush Set contains 8 essential face and eye brushes featuring anti-bacterial, extra-soft fibres. Each brush is vegan-certified and designed to work with all skin types.',148.00,'ITC-BRU-HL8',25,true,true,ARRAY['brush-set','it-cosmetics','8-piece','luxe','anti-bacterial']),
((SELECT id FROM brands WHERE slug='bobbi-brown'),14,'Classic Brush Collection','bobbi-classic-brush-collection','6-piece classic collection of face and eye essentials.','Bobbi Brown Classic Brush Collection includes 6 essential brushes used by Bobbi Brown herself: foundation, concealer, blush, eye shadow, eye liner and brow brushes. Premium quality for professional results.',195.00,'BB-BRU-CBC',20,true,true,ARRAY['brush-set','bobbi-brown','classic','professional','6-piece']),
((SELECT id FROM brands WHERE slug='tom-ford-beauty'),14,'Eye Brush Set','tomford-eye-brush-set','4-piece luxury eye brush set in polished chrome handles.','Tom Ford Eye Brush Set features 4 exquisitely crafted eye brushes with polished chrome and black lacquer handles. The collection covers lid packing, blending, liner and crease detailing.',220.00,'TF-BRU-EBS',15,true,true,ARRAY['brush-set','tom-ford','eye','luxury','4-piece'])
